videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald gives them the lead on a 4th-down QB sneak.
videos.headline: Mississippi State scores on 4th-down QB sneak

videos.headline: Fitzgerald QB sneaks a TD for 2nd time in two drives
